      "id": "stage-01",
      "order": 1,
      "title": "Decimales y %",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Decimales y %</title>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .example h4, .task h4 { margin-top: 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n    code.k { background:#f7f7f7; padding:.15rem .35rem; border-radius:4px; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<h1>Decimales y porcentajes</h1>\n<div><span class=\"badge\">Eje</span> Fracciones en contexto cotidiano</div>\n<p>El porcentaje es “de cada 100”. 25% = 25/100 = 0.25.</p>\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Ejemplo</h4>\n  <p>Descuento del 10% a $50: 10% de 50 es 5 → pagas <strong>$45</strong>.</p>\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
      "formulas": [
